mitchellfoundation.org/news/the-joan-mitchell-foundation-announces-the-2013-painters-sculptors-grant-re''Annual 2013 Painters & Sculptors Grant, The Joan Mitchell Foundation, New York, New York, 2013'']\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20140312225320/http://www.expochicago.com/sites/default/files/EXPO%20CHGO%202013%20Prize%20Release_09.20.13.pdf ''Andree Stone Emerging Artist Prize, Expo Chicago, Chicago, IL, 2013'']\n*''The Marie Walsh Sharpe Foundation Fellowship, 2012-2013''\n*''Henry Street Settlement/Abrons Art Center AIRspace Residency, 2011-2012''\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20090526052307/http://www.macdowellcolony.org/artists-indexfellows.php ''The Robert Motherwell Fellowship, The MacDowell Colony, 2011-2012'']\n*[http://yaddo.org/yaddo/ArtistsLists.shtml ''Yaddo Fellowship, 2011'']\n*[http://www.nj.com/news/index.ssf/2011/02/nj_arts_council_awards_artist.html ''New Jersey State Council on the Arts Fellowship, 2011'']\n*[http://arts.vcu.edu/paintingprintmaking/fellowship/ ''VCUarts Fountainhead Arts Fellowship at Virginia Commonwealth University 2008-2009'']\n\n==Further reading==\n*[http://www.artspeak.nyc/home/2017/5/6/amy-feldman ''Osman Can Yerebakan, Amy Feldman - Nerve Reserve, Artspeak, May 6, 2017'']\n*[http://amyfeldmanstudio.com/wp-content/uploads/new_york_catalog_kunstmuseum_bonn.pdf''Christoph Schreier, \"Painting as Pictorial Art New York Painting in the 21st Century\", Kunstmuseum Bonn, Hirmer, 2015'']\n*[http://www.thenation.com/article/196161/zeitgeist-no-zeitgeist# ''Barry Schwabsky, \"The Zeitgeist of No Zeitgeist\", The Nation, January 26, 2015'']\n*[https://www.artforum.com/index.php?pn=picks&id=51657&view=print ''Amanda Dalla Villa Adams, Amy Feldman, Artforum, 2015'']\n*[http://moussemagazine.it/amy-feldman-pascual-sisto-brand-new-gallery-2015/ ''Andrianna Campbell, Amy Feldman, Mousse, 2015'']\n*[https://www.artforum.com/print/reviews/201410/amy-feldman-49164''Michael Wilson, Amy Feldman, Artforum, 2014'']\n*[http://hyperallergic.co